						//- Hidden percent is needed to take space.
						| #[span.loader__percent__hidden 100%]
						//- Hidden percents are shown one by one with fancy animation to create effect of a moving progress. After animation is finished, loader is stuck ata random value between 60 and 90. After the last intro image is loaded the intro appears.
