					| Accommodations
				p.paragraphs__item__text
					| We have three accommocations for travelers in Seoul, Korea. The places have young and createive SEOUL vibes. Our guests always give us great insights for travelling overall. As an OTA, having accommodations help us to serve better for your guest as well.
