				.decor__flying_word_box.decor__flying_word_box--top(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-2em); ", data-top-bottom="transform: translateY(5em);")
					.decor__flying_word_img_box
						img.decor__flying_word_img(src="img/etc/big_word--unique--black.svg")
		.paragraphs_box.paragraphs_box--middle.paragraphs_box--black
			.paragraphs_box__decor_word_container
				.decor__flying_word_box.decor__flying_word_box--bottom(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-2em); ", data-top-bottom="transform: translateY(5em);")
					.decor__flying_word_img_box
						img.decor__flying_word_img(src="img/etc/big_word--unique--white.svg")
			img.paragraphs_box_img.paragraphs_box_img--left(src="img/pictures/mockups/left2.png", data-bottom-top="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(20%); ", data-top-bottom="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(-5%);")
			img.paragraphs_box_img.paragraphs_box_img--right.js-appearing-content(src="img/pictures/mockups/right.png", data-bottom-top="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(-10%); ", data-top-bottom="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(5%);", data-appear-top-offset="200")
			.paragraphs__item.paragraphs__item--no_number.js-appearing-content
				h2.paragraphs__item__title.paragraphs__item__title--cream
					| Learn, Execute,#[br]Improve, Repeat#[br]and Automate
				p.paragraphs__item__text.paragraphs__item__text--white
					| Undefinedist is Group of young and passionate people who want to solve problems. We learn things fast and execute it right away. Then gradually improve the process and quality. Repeat this process untill we are statisfied. Lastly, Automate it and move on.
				.paragraphs_box_big_line(data-bottom-top="transform: scaleY(0.5);", data-center-bottom="transform: scaleY(1);")
				.paragraphs_box_line(data-bottom-top="transform: scaleY(0);", data-center-bottom="transform: scaleY(1);")
			a.paragraphs__button.button.button--cream-border(href=links.premium, target="_blank")
				| Live Preview
		.paragraphs_box.paragraphs_box--bottom
			.paragraphs__item.paragraphs__item--03.js-appearing-content(data-bottom-top="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(20%); opacity: 0;", data-top-bottom="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(-20%);" data--100-bottom="opacity:1;")
				h2.paragraphs__item__title
					| Software & Design
					.paragraphs_title_line(data-bottom-top="transform: scaleY(0);", data-center-bottom="transform: scaleY(1);")
					.paragraphs_title_big_line(data-bottom-top="transform: scaleY(0);", data-center-bottom="transform: scaleY(1);")
					.paragraphs_title_square.decor_square
				p.paragraphs__item__text
					| We build useful and automated software to help our customers. Great software can be changed easily to improve for our partners.
					| Design every products with createive yet pratical visualization. Every compartments has their reason with beauty visual.
				span.paragraphs__item__number(data-bottom-top="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(5%); opacity: 0;", data-top-bottom="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(-20%);" data--200-bottom="opacity:1;")
					| 03
			.paragraphs__item.paragraphs__item--04.js-appearing-content(data-bottom-top="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(20%); opacity: 0;", data-top-bottom="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(-20%);" data--100-bottom="opacity:1;")
				.paragraphs_box_line(data-bottom-top="transform: scaleY(0);", data-center-bottom="transform: scaleY(1);")
				h2.paragraphs__item__title
					| Creative & Craftsmanship
				p.paragraphs__item__text
					| Not using generallized and normal product. We always build our own tools to create and solve problem to be more sophisticated.
				span.paragraphs__item__number(data-bottom-top="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(5%); opacity: 0;", data-top-bottom="transform: translateZ(0) translateY(-20%);" data--200-bottom="opacity:1;")
					| 04

